---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="High School Sports Banquet Planning Guide" description="Plan unforgettable high school sports banquets, senior nights, award ceremonies, and graduations. Free guides, checklists, and expert planning resources for coaches and parents.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The Ultimate Resource for Planning High School Sports Celebrations</h1>
      <p>Free expert guides, checklists, and decoration ideas for sports banquets, senior nights, award ceremonies, and graduation parties. Built for coaches, by people who get it.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-primary">Start Planning Your Banquet →</a>
        <a href="#guides" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse All Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Everything You Need to Plan an Unforgettable Athletic Celebration</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 1rem;color:var(--text-light);">
        Whether you're a coach, booster club parent, athletic director, or team mom — you've come to the right place. This isn't a store. It's a library of practical, field-tested planning resources built specifically for high school athletics.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guide Cards -->
  <section id="guides" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Four Key Events, One Trusted Resource</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏆 Sports Banquet Guide</h3>
          <p>Venue selection, menu planning, program structure, seating arrangements, and centerpiece ideas. The complete playbook.</p>
          <a href="/banquet-planning/" class="card-link">Read the Guide →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>⭐ Senior Night Guide</h3>
          <p>Ceremony scripts, parent speech templates, senior gift ideas, and special moments that make the night unforgettable.</p>
          <a href="/senior-night/" class="card-link">Plan Senior Night →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🎓 Graduation Party Guide</h3>
          <p>Themes, catering, decorations, photo booth setups, and party flow planning for your graduate's celebration.</p>
          <a href="/graduation-party/" class="card-link">Party Planning →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏅 Award Ceremony Guide</h3>
          <p>Award categories, presentation order, coach awards, and creating moments that matter for every athlete.</p>
          <a href="/award-ceremony/" class="card-link">Ceremony Planning →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Decoration Section -->
  <section style="background:var(--bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Make Your Tables Unforgettable</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center;max-width:650px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;color:var(--text-light);">
        The centerpiece is the heart of every banquet table. Custom 3D printed sports centerpieces capture your team's identity in a way generic decorations never can.
      </p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏈 Football Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>Available in multiple sizes — 8.75", 11.5", and 12" footballs in your team colors with optional personalization.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/football-graduation-centerpiece-8-3-4-football" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏀 Basketball Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>7" and 9" basketballs with optional team name and player number personalization. Perfect for banquet tables.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/basketball-banquet-table-centerpiece-7-ball" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>⚽ Soccer Ball Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>8" custom soccer balls designed in your team colors with personalization for banquets and graduation parties.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/custom-soccer-ball-centerpiece-8-soccer-ball-graduation-party-birthday" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏐 Volleyball Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>8" volleyball centerpieces with team personalization. Available in multiple color options for your program.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/volleyball-banquet-table-centerpiece-8-volleyball" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>📣 Cheerleading Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>Megaphones, pom poms, and cheer awards — custom 3D printed in your squad's colors. Great for banquet tables.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/cheerleader-megaphone-cheer-banquet-table-centerpiece-cheerleading" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🏃 Track & Field Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>Flying track shoes, high jump, hurdles, long jump, and javelin centerpieces for track banquets and graduation.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/flying-track-shoe-track-shoe-with-wings-banquet-table-centerpiece" class="card-link" target="_blank">View Options →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Free Tools -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Free Planning Tools to Save You Time</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>📋 Banquet Checklist</h3>
          <p>Printable 8-week timeline checklist. Know exactly what to do and when.</p>
          <a href="/checklist/" class="card-link">Get the Checklist →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
          <p>Quick answers to the most common banquet planning questions.</p>
          <a href="/faq/" class="card-link">Browse FAQs →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>🎨 Decoration Ideas</h3>
          <p>Budget-friendly to premium decoration options for every type of celebration.</p>
          <a href="/decorations/" class="card-link">Explore Ideas →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Email Capture -->
  <section style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="email-capture">
        <h3>📥 Get the Free Banquet Planning Checklist</h3>
        <p>Printable PDF with the complete 8-week timeline. Enter your email and we'll send it right over.</p>
        <form action="#" method="post">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Me the Checklist</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Breadcrumb Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "SportsBanquetGuide.com",
    "url": "https://sportsbanquetguide.com"
  }
  </script>
</MainLayout>
